/* eslint-disable */
import girl1 from '../assets/svg/testimonials/girl1.svg'
import girl2 from '../assets/svg/testimonials/girl2.svg'
import girl3 from '../assets/svg/testimonials/girl3.svg'
import boy1 from '../assets/svg/testimonials/boy1.svg'
import boy2 from '../assets/svg/testimonials/boy2.svg'
import boy3 from '../assets/svg/testimonials/boy3.svg'



export const testimonialsData = [
    {
        id: 1,
        name: 'Mujtaba',
        title: 'Google PPCier',
        text: "Athul is a true full stack developer and I always reach out to him for the most complex problems. His ability to troubleshoot the problem with ease and perfection is my favorite skill set of him. I will give him extra points for his understanding on the digital marketing ecosystem which is very rare to find in most of the developers.",
        image: boy2
    },
    {
        id: 2,
        name: 'Richard Luna',
        title: 'ProtectedHarbor- Client of Athul',
        text: "Athul is a hard worker and a good programmer. His specialty was communicating with the end user and understanding exactly what is needed and why. Athul would then take that input and turn it into a program plan and then he correctly executed the work. He has a great personality and is easy going.",
        image: boy3
    },
    {
        id: 3,
        name: 'Zeehan Akthar',
        title: 'Business Analyst - Emirates NBD',
        text: "Athul firstly is a wonderful person. His calm, hardworking and helpful attitude spreads positivity on the work floor, We have worked with each other for 2 years under different projects, His ability to understand the problem and give quick and apt solutions is just what a Full Stack Developer should possess and adds immense value to the team with his creativity.",
        image: boy1
    },
    {
        id: 4,
        name: 'Joey Tribbiani',
        title: 'Actor',
        text: "Making my portfolio with this helped me get my role as 'Dr. Drake Ramoray' in 'Days Of Our Lives'. You guys are the best !",
        image: boy3
    },
    {
        id: 5,
        name: 'Rachel Green',
        title: 'Sales Executive',
        text: 'Ralph Lauren was one of the best things that ever happened to me. My portfolio made that dream happen. I owe you guys.',
        image: girl3
    },
    {
        id: 6,
        name: 'Ross Geller',
        title: 'Paleontologist',
        text: "Be it 'Rocks' or 'Bones', you need a website to display it. This is it. Great work guys !",
        image: boy3
    }
]
